name: pixelcraft
author: Sh1penfire and pankiwi
description:
[red]panini return[]
A Pixelcraft. A new way to play Mindustry. A mod that allows you to play with a different main resource, leaving copper and lead in the dust. Based on Mindustry classic, adds a new tech tree, several new sectors to a a new planet, 7 different types of turrets and much much more...
